group was exposed to the scent of lavender oil while a control group was simply monitored. The study found that the group which inhaled lavender essential oil for thirty minutes was significantly calmer, showing less signs of stress. This shows the impact that lavender essential oil can have on the anxiety levels of cats. <br><br>However, due to the sensitive nature of cats, you should use lavender oil with caution, observing them regularly for any adverse effects.
